sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant GUI
    participant Service
    participant Scheduler
    
    User->>GUI: Launch EXE
    alt First Run
        GUI->>GUI: Setup master passphrase
    else Normal Run
        GUI->>Crypto: Unlock credential vault
    end
    GUI->>DB: Load switches/schedules
    GUI->>Scheduler: Start scheduler
    Scheduler->>Service: Execute scheduled backups
    loop Every 30s
        GUI->>Dashboard: Refresh monitoring
    end
    User->>GUI: Close window
    GUI->>Scheduler: Stop scheduler (if not service mode)
